50:32.042 --> 50:33.792
<i>I know that you're frightened</i>

50:33.827 --> 50:36.912
<i>and there are many decisions</i>
<i>I can't prepare you for,</i>

50:36.964 --> 50:38.964
<i>but you must immediately</i>
<i>tell the hospital</i>

50:38.999 --> 50:42.000
<i>and the funeral director</i>
<i>that I'm to be interred intact</i>

50:42.002 --> 50:44.469
<i>in the family plot</i>
<i>in West Laurel.</i>

50:44.505 --> 50:48.056
<i>Uncle William has the details</i>
