50:49.226 --> 50:50.676
<i>I've also enclosed a portrait</i>

50:50.728 --> 50:53.562
<i>from the 1968 Republican</i>
<i>Winter Gala.</i>

50:53.597 --> 50:56.848
<i>The blue chiffon I wore</i>
<i>is my very favorite.</i>

50:56.850 --> 51:00.769
<i>I hung it in a gold garment bag in
