51:02.439 --> 51:04.740
<i>Please bring them the lipstick</i>
<i>from my handbag</i>

51:04.775 --> 51:07.159
<i>and remind them</i>
<i>how I like to wear my hair.</i>

51:08.579 --> 51:10.529
<i>Will you show them the picture?</i>

51:12.866 --> 51:15.367
<i>Sally, I always</i>
<i>worried about you</i>

51:15.419 --> 51:18.503
<i>because you march</i>
<i>to the beat of your own drum.</i>

51:18.539 --> 51:22.007
<i>But now I know that's good.</i>

51:22.042 --> 51:24.543
<i>I know your life</i>
